1. *Tom* je učinio svoj deo posla. (He did his part.)
2. On je bio veoma zadovoljan što je *Tom* uspeo. (He was very pleased that Tom succeeded.)
3. *Tome* svemu treba dodati još nešto. (Something else needs to be added to that.)
4. Oni su se razišli po *tome* što je rečeno. (They parted after that was said.)
5. Svi smo čekali da *Tom* završi. (We all waited for Tom to finish.)
6. *Tome* se treba odati pažnja. (Attention should be paid to that.)